snippet.title: DAWN - Announcement Trailer |  Steam (PC)
snippet.description:
WITNESS THE DAWN! A new horror stirs in The American West.
-

 It isn’t an ordinary night. The storm outside was just the start. The wind. The rain. 

An omen of things to come.

-
Attempt to escape and survive the horror as one of two characters, solo, or together with a friend.
--

https://store.steampowered.com/app/3198880/DAWN/

CHECK OUT AND PLAY ITS DEMO MONDAY, OCTOBER 14TH (as part of STEAM NEXT FEST)

https://store.steampowered.com/app/3273270/DAWN_CALM_BEFORE_THE_STORM__DEMO/
